  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 180.0,
      "end_time": 3500.0,
      "text": "Deliberate practice is a mindful and highly structured"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 3500.0,
      "end_time": 5680.0,
      "text": "form of learning by doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5860.0,
      "end_time": 9120.0,
      "text": "It’s a process of continued experimentation"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 9120.0,
      "end_time": 11820.0,
      "text": "to first achieve mastery and eventually full"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 11820.0,
      "end_time": 14560.0,
      "text": "automaticity of a specific skill."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 14820.0,
      "end_time": 18680.0,
      "text": "A 2014 study published in Psychological Science"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 18680.0,
      "end_time": 20880.0,
      "text": "argues that it can increase our performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 20880.0,
      "end_time": 27460.0,
      "text": "by 26% in games, 21% in music and 18% in sports."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 27460.0,
      "end_time": 30440.0,
      "text": "Here are some tips on how to do it well."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 31880.0,
      "end_time": 35520.0,
      "text": "Define Success and Drill Deliberately"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 35880.0,
      "end_time": 38460.0,
      "text": "Define all the elements you need to practice"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38460.0,
      "end_time": 40180.0,
      "text": "to become successful."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 40180.0,
      "end_time": 42620.0,
      "text": "Then drill each element deliberately,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42620.0,
      "end_time": 44040.0,
      "text": "one after the other."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44160.0,
      "end_time": 46840.0,
      "text": "In Tennis, that could be first your serves"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 46840.0,
      "end_time": 48660.0,
      "text": "and then later your leg work."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 48840.0,
      "end_time": 51440.0,
      "text": "If you want to become a professional barista,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 51440.0,
      "end_time": 54260.0,
      "text": "first perfect your moves to make the espresso,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 54260.0,
      "end_time": 57460.0,
      "text": "then your skills to serve the ideal coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58920.0,
      "end_time": 62300.0,
      "text": "Plan, Reflect and Take Notes"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62620.0,
      "end_time": 64620.0,
      "text": "Plan out your practice routine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64620.00000000001,
      "end_time": 66460.0,
      "text": "for example in a notebook."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 66460.0,
      "end_time": 67920.0,
      "text": "After each session,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 67920.0,
      "end_time": 70720.0,
      "text": "reflect and write down what you've discovered:"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70720.0,
      "end_time": 71820.0,
      "text": "What worked?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 71820.0,
      "end_time": 72960.0,
      "text": "What didn’t?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 73160.0,
      "end_time": 75240.0,
      "text": "The idea is to get a clear sense"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 75240.0,
      "end_time": 78200.0,
      "text": "of how a particular session improves your skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78360.0,
      "end_time": 81500.0,
      "text": "and then to experiment to find new and ever better way"
