      "text": "practice slow and correctly."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 92320.0,
      "end_time": 94020.0,
      "text": "If we move too fast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 94020.0,
      "end_time": 97280.0,
      "text": "we risk learning and internalizing the wrong skills,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 97280.0,
      "end_time": 99780.0,
      "text": "which can bring terrible consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 100040.0,
      "end_time": 103900.0,
      "text": "To achieve mastery, our brain needs time to develop."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103900.0,
      "end_time": 107340.0,
      "text": "So start slow and then gradually increase the speed"
